</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_443" id="220v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen von Gych <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, gesessen czu Elrn</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                        Elspet, des Friczen Schoszharts, und Gerhawse, des
                            <expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> Herbsts, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> eliche wirtynne von iren und
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> wirte wegen, <add>die
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> niht
                                <expan>anh<ex>eim</ex></expan> sind</add>, wie ir in aufgehalten
                        habt mit namen <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Schoszhart und
                            <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan> xxiiii rycz bapyrs und
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Herbst und <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan> viii ring drocz und xxii stück messings; und
                        also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burger <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan> bede
                        yede für sich und iren wirte vor uns czu den heiligen behabt, daz die
                                <expan>eges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> habe ir und anderr
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> sey, also daz kein auszman weder teil noch
                        gemein daran niht hab. Hyrümb <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir habe
                            <expan>ungehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vollgen lasset. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>ascens<ex>ionis</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan>
<expan>a<ex>nno</ex></expan> xxii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
